## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c461e-140">下列範例會建立<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>從<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>使用的物件<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>，它定義的陣列<xref:System.String>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c461e-140">The following example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> object that uses a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>, which is defined by an array of <xref:System.String> objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c461e-141">辨識引擎使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>建立會辨識片語 「 色彩紅色綠色的藍色零 」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c461e-141">A recognition engine using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> created will recognize the phrase "color red green blue zero".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c461e-142">語意<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase>所傳回包含辨識<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>與<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A>的 「 藍色紅色綠色 」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c461e-142">The semantics of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> returned by recognition will contain a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> with a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue.Value%2A> of "red green blue".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c461e-143">您可以存取<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>使用 「 程式碼 」 標記。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c461e-143">You can access the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> using the "code" tag.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c461e-144">由於`SemanticResultValue("zero", 5)`附加至<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>，根<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>物件中<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase>會有 5 個值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c461e-144">Because of the `SemanticResultValue("zero", 5)` appended to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>, the root <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> object in the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> will have a value of 5.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void keyTest()   
{  
  // Say "color red green blue zero"  
  GrammarBuilder gb = new GrammarBuilder("color") +  
                        new SemanticResultKey("code",   
                          (new string[] {"red", "green", "blue"})) +  
                        new SemanticResultValue("zero", 5);  
  Grammar g = new Grammar(gb);  
  g.Name = "keyTest";  
  _recognizer.LoadGrammar(g);  
}  
```

  
  
